{"lemma":"مَسْأَلَةٌ","slug":"مَسْأَلَةٌ","root":"س.#.ل","root_slug":"س-_-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/س-_-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":4},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n18591"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8E%D8%B3%D9%92%D8%A3%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of سَأَلَ (saʔala) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"question","tags":["dated"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"issue, problem, point in question, thesis"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"request, begging"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/mas.ʔa.la/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n18591","headword_ar":"مَسْاَلَةٌ","root":"sA^l","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", an inf. n. of 1, is tropically used in the sense of a pass. part. n. [with the noun qualified by it understood; meaning (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thing asked;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a question; a problem,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"proposition; a matter,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an affair, proposed for decision"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"determination"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (TA:) and the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"masaAy^ilu","text_ar":"مَسَايِلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb, TA.) So in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taEal~amotu masoA^alapF","text_ar":"تَعَلَّمْتُ مَسْاَلَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I learned a"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1284},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"question,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"problem,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]. (TA.) The saying, in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kariha AlmasaAy^ila waEaAbahaA","text_ar":"كَرِهَ المَسَايِلَ وَعَابَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"means (assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mohammad)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disliked and discommended"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"subtile questions, such as are needless."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suw^olN","text_ar":"سُوْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": ―         -b3-  and see 4."}],"source_refs":["TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}